This is the source repository of the MIR task-based runtime system library. To get started with using MIR, please read docs/MIR_UG.pdf. The name MIR is inspired by Mir Publishers from Moscow. I enjoyed Mir books on electronics and geometry during my childhood.

Author: Ananya Muddukrishna.

E-mail: ananya@kth.se.

Contributors: Peter A. Jonsson.

Selected Publications:

[1] Muddukrishna, Ananya, P. A. Jonsson, and M. Brorsson, “Characterizing task-based OpenMP programs,” PLoS ONE, vol. 10, 04 2015.

[2] Muddukrishna, Ananya, P. A. Jonsson, and M. Brorsson, “Locality-aware task scheduling and data distribution for OpenMP programs on NUMA systems and manycore processors,” Scientific Programming, no. 981759, 2015.
